{"tid":1588050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［打蛇隨棍上］將 獅鳥 威力發揮到極致","createTime":"2019-09-22T16:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T13:36:18.000Z","uid":281293,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3429dad9d329edf09c47df37ae7fd2a827fbe690","tid":1588050,"uid":281293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:02:22.000Z","msg":"獅鳥除咗解決當前問題<br />\n大家都知獅鳥係要俾藍屍知挑釁係有後果<br />\n所當獅鳥現身就要大力文宣<br />\n去d藍屍page宣掦下神獸之威<br />\n<br />\n本人覺得個宗旨係要散播失敗主義，同blame the victim <br />\n<br />\n藍屍page會讚揚d仆街英勇，藍屍會同情d仆街。<br />\n所以要帶風向，去扮藍屍，製造恐慌，指責傷者愚蠢。<br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n1. 依家d黑衣人唔係人咁品架啦，走去撩人係好勇，但係你又唔係好好打，執返條命算好啦，唔好咁笨得架<br />\n<br />\n2. 古語有云，閒事莫理，眾地莫企，中國人嘅哲學真理真係冇錯，大家見人多就快d走唔好講咁多野啦<br />\n<br />\n以上未必對d癲佬有用，但係對d婦孺係會有心理影響"},{"pid":"6e5f22dcc4ab152d8fafa10ef58d22b0cb578fd3","tid":1588050,"uid":281293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:06:38.000Z","msg":"打心理戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8dea03a1905d6258c1438a6daa586c1096b8d28","tid":1588050,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"545993ce3f12712c40e3ab54a8d070e547f08e1b","tid":1588050,"uid":281293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:08:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62ae0f45c64f4da2827be42a161ecaeb78965b9c","tid":1588050,"uid":281293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:15:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f9f8ba797ab1f5cd4e10f91c8d1b7b2cf112a8","tid":1588050,"uid":68009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:21:37.000